body: why some phone number failed with reason "no_routes" while some phone number works ok

comment_data.body: Because WhatsApp has some issues with reaching certain cell networks to send SMS messages.
But, with the same phone number, it works well on android cell phones.
Additional, it works well with Official whatsapp apk
